Wilmington.Gwinhurst, Delaware:
Gwinhurst is an unincorporated community in New Castle County, Delaware, United States. Its altitude is 98 feet (30 m), and it is located at 39°47′30″N 75°28′44″W (39.7917797, -75.4788080).
A part of Brandywine Hundred, Gwinhurst is located between Claymont and the incorporated town of Bellefonte.
